55:36.083 --> 55:39.758
Oh, that's, um, that's Jimmy's ring.

55:40.750 --> 55:42.343
The boy's a damn fool.

55:52.417 --> 55:53.919
(WHISPERS) God, you're beautiful.

55:56.375 --> 55:59.299
♪ I want to tell the world, baby

55:59.417 --> 56:02.136
