57:06.167 --> 57:07.464
What?

57:07.583 --> 57:08.709
But here's the thing, Dave.

57:08.833 --> 57:10.085
Yeah, the line's pretty bad.

57:10.208 --> 57:11.255
No escort.

57:11.375 --> 57:13.503
